[src:xxe-prevention/xml-external-entity-prevention-cheat-sheet] Set these values to true to disable inline DTDs completely.
[src:xxe-prevention/xml-external-entity-prevention-cheat-sheet] Alternatively, you can set the `DtdProcessing` property to `Ignore`, which will not throw an exception on encountering a `<!DOCTYPE>` element but will simply skip over it and not process it.
