[src:xxe-prevention/xml-external-entity-prevention-cheat-sheet] For .NET Framework version ≥4.5.2, XPathNavigator is **safe by default**.
[src:xxe-prevention/xml-external-entity-prevention-cheat-sheet] `System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform` (an XML transformer) is safe by default as long as the parser it's given is safe.
